  ('customs-7fec267e-moex-00147', 'customs-7fec267e', 'customs-7fec267e-moex-112-6948958a', 'sub-customs-7fec267e-01', NULL, 'single_choice', '當某一商品的製造過程中會產生水污染的外部成本，此時的市場均衡價格和數量與社會最適的價格和數 量相比較時，下列敘述何者正確？', '["市場均衡價格高於社會最適價格，市場均衡數量也高於社會最適數量", "市場均衡價格高於社會最適價格，市場均衡數量則低於社會最適數量", "市場均衡價格低於社會最適價格，市場均衡數量則高於社會最適數量", "市場均衡價格低於社會最適價格，市場均衡數量也低於社會最適數量"]'::jsonb, 2, NULL, TRUE, 'official', TRUE, 1, '{"parser_version": "moex_license_v1.0", "parsed_at": "2026-04-25T12:22:21+00:00", "source_pdf_sha1": "1e70fcf8ae3b", "answer_pdf_sha1": "aee6e6b22814", "source_family": "moex-gov-tw", "moex": {"exam_code": "112050", "c": "141", "s": "0904", "q": "1"}, "raw_section_label": "本試題為單一選擇題", "subject": "經濟學概要", "year": "112", "exam_name": "112年公務人員特種考試關務人員考試、身心障礙人員考試、國軍上校以上軍官轉任公務人員考試", "original_question_number": 27, "answer_corrected": false, "flags": [], "civil_slug": "customs", "civil_category": "一般行政"}'::jsonb, NULL),
  ('customs-7fec267e-moex-00148', 'customs-7fec267e', 'customs-7fec267e-moex-112-6948958a', 'sub-customs-7fec267e-01', NULL, 'single_choice', '下列有關公共財的敘述，何者錯誤？', '["具有非敵對性的特性", "具有非排他性的特性", "容易產生搭便車（freerider）的現象", "只能由公部門的政府提供"]'::jsonb, 3, NULL, TRUE, 'official', TRUE, 1, '{"parser_version": "moex_license_v1.0", "parsed_at": "2026-04-25T12:22:21+00:00", "source_pdf_sha1": "1e70fcf8ae3b", "answer_pdf_sha1": "aee6e6b22814", "source_family": "moex-gov-tw", "moex": {"exam_code": "112050", "c": "141", "s": "0904", "q": "1"}, "raw_section_label": "本試題為單一選擇題", "subject": "經濟學概要", "year": "112", "exam_name": "112年公務人員特種考試關務人員考試、身心障礙人員考試、國軍上校以上軍官轉任公務人員考試", "original_question_number": 28, "answer_corrected": false, "flags": [], "civil_slug": "customs", "civil_category": "一般行政"}'::jsonb, NULL),
  ('customs-7fec267e-moex-00149', 'customs-7fec267e', 'customs-7fec267e-moex-112-6948958a', 'sub-customs-7fec267e-01', NULL, 'single_choice', '假設某國只生產蔬菜和魚兩種商品，且中間投入成本微小到可以被忽略。數量的單位是公噸，價格的單位 是每公噸萬元。下表是2019年與2020年，這兩種商品的產量與單位售價資料。以2019年為基期，在這 兩年之間，GDP平減指數（GDPdeflator）上升了多少？ 2019年 2020年 商品項目 數量 價格 數量 價格 蔬菜 250 $2 400 $2.5 魚 1000 $1.6 2000 $2', '["65%", "42%", "36%", "25%"]'::jsonb, 3, NULL, TRUE, 'official', TRUE, 1, '{"parser_version": "moex_license_v1.0", "parsed_at": "2026-04-25T12:22:21+00:00", "source_pdf_sha1": "1e70fcf8ae3b", "answer_pdf_sha1": "aee6e6b22814", "source_family": "moex-gov-tw", "moex": {"exam_code": "112050", "c": "141", "s": "0904", "q": "1"}, "raw_section_label": "本試題為單一選擇題", "subject": "經濟學概要", "year": "112", "exam_name": "112年公務人員特種考試關務人員考試、身心障礙人員考試、國軍上校以上軍官轉任公務人員考試", "original_question_number": 29, "answer_corrected": false, "flags": [], "civil_slug": "customs", "civil_category": "一般行政"}'::jsonb, NULL),
  ('customs-7fec267e-moex-00150', 'customs-7fec267e', 'customs-7fec267e-moex-112-6948958a', 'sub-customs-7fec267e-01', NULL, 'single_choice', '在新冠肺炎疫情衝擊某國經濟下，其廠商通報無薪假人數已達 1.5 萬人，若其他條件不變，該國目前有', '["", "", "", ""]'::jsonb, 2, NULL, FALSE, 'official', TRUE, 1, '{"parser_version": "moex_license_v1.0", "parsed_at": "2026-04-25T12:22:21+00:00", "source_pdf_sha1": "1e70fcf8ae3b", "answer_pdf_sha1": "aee6e6b22814", "source_family": "moex-gov-tw", "moex": {"exam_code": "112050", "c": "141", "s": "0904", "q": "1"}, "raw_section_label": "本試題為單一選擇題", "subject": "經濟學概要", "year": "112", "exam_name": "112年公務人員特種考試關務人員考試、身心障礙人員考試、國軍上校以上軍官轉任公務人員考試", "original_question_number": 30, "answer_corrected": false, "flags": ["incomplete_options"], "civil_slug": "customs", "civil_category": "一般行政"}'::jsonb, NULL),
  ('customs-7fec267e-moex-00151', 'customs-7fec267e', 'customs-7fec267e-moex-112-6948958a', 'sub-customs-7fec267e-01', NULL, 'single_choice', '5萬人處於就業狀態、57萬人處於失業狀態、832.5萬人屬於非勞動力（outofthelaborforce），則 該國失業率（unemploymentrate）是多少？', '["5.17%", "4.93%", "4.80%", "4.55%"]'::jsonb, 0, NULL, FALSE, 'official', TRUE, 1, '{"parser_version": "moex_license_v1.0", "parsed_at": "2026-04-25T12:22:21+00:00", "source_pdf_sha1": "1e70fcf8ae3b", "answer_pdf_sha1": "aee6e6b22814", "source_family": "moex-gov-tw", "moex": {"exam_code": "112050", "c": "141", "s": "0904", "q": "1"}, "raw_section_label": "本試題為單一選擇題", "subject": "經濟學概要", "year": "112", "exam_name": "112年公務人員特種考試關務人員考試、身心障礙人員考試、國軍上校以上軍官轉任公務人員考試", "original_question_number": 1130, "answer_corrected": false, "flags": ["answer_missing"], "civil_slug": "customs", "civil_category": "一般行政"}'::jsonb, NULL),
  ('customs-7fec267e-moex-00152', 'customs-7fec267e', 'customs-7fec267e-moex-112-6948958a', 'sub-customs-7fec267e-01', NULL, 'single_choice', '根據行政院主計總處定義，所謂沮喪勞動力（discouragedworker）是指：', '["曾經找工作，但一直找不到，所以就先放棄找工作的人", "在工作中得不到成就感，因而離開職場的人", "想找工作，且積極在找工作，但卻找不到的人", "工作績效較差的人"]'::jsonb, 0, NULL, TRUE, 'official', TRUE, 1, '{"parser_version": "moex_license_v1.0", "parsed_at": "2026-04-25T12:22:21+00:00", "source_pdf_sha1": "1e70fcf8ae3b", "answer_pdf_sha1": "aee6e6b22814", "source_family": "moex-gov-tw", "moex": {"exam_code": "112050", "c": "141", "s": "0904", "q": "1"}, "raw_section_label": "本試題為單一選擇題", "subject": "經濟學概要", "year": "112", "exam_name": "112年公務人員特種考試關務人員考試、身心障礙人員考試、國軍上校以上軍官轉任公務人員考試", "original_question_number": 31, "answer_corrected": false, "flags": [], "civil_slug": "customs", "civil_category": "一般行政"}'::jsonb, NULL),
  ('customs-7fec267e-moex-00153', 'customs-7fec267e', 'customs-7fec267e-moex-112-6948958a', 'sub-customs-7fec267e-01', NULL, 'single_choice', '有關國民生產毛額（grossnationalproduct,GNP）敘述，下列何者錯誤？', '["GNP是指一國全體人民、在一定期間內，所生產之所有最終商品與勞務（finalgoodsandservices）的 名目市場價值（nominalmarketvalues）", "使用市場價值（market values）來衡量GNP的一個問題是：有一些有用的商品和服務並沒有在市場上 交易", "GNP必然大於國內生產毛額（grossdomesticproduct）", "一國GNP愈高，其經濟福祉（economicwelfare）未必愈高"]'::jsonb, 2, NULL, TRUE, 'official', TRUE, 1, '{"parser_version": "moex_license_v1.0", "parsed_at": "2026-04-25T12:22:21+00:00", "source_pdf_sha1": "1e70fcf8ae3b", "answer_pdf_sha1": "aee6e6b22814", "source_family": "moex-gov-tw", "moex": {"exam_code": "112050", "c": "141", "s": "0904", "q": "1"}, "raw_section_label": "本試題為單一選擇題", "subject": "經濟學概要", "year": "112", "exam_name": "112年公務人員特種考試關務人員考試、身心障礙人員考試、國軍上校以上軍官轉任公務人員考試", "original_question_number": 32, "answer_corrected": false, "flags": [], "civil_slug": "customs", "civil_category": "一般行政"}'::jsonb, NULL),
  ('customs-7fec267e-moex-00154', 'customs-7fec267e', 'customs-7fec267e-moex-112-6948958a', 'sub-customs-7fec267e-01', NULL, 'single_choice', '在缺乏生產力成長（productivitygrowth）的Solow成長模型裡，當經濟體達到穩定狀態（steady-state）時，則：', '["平均每位勞工的消費（consumptionperworker）仍會隨時間而變動，但資本-勞動比例（capital-laborratio） 是常數", "平均每位勞工的消費是常數，但資本-勞動比例會隨時間而變動", "平均每位勞工的消費與資本-勞動比例均是常數", "資本與勞動呈現相反的變動方向"]'::jsonb, 2, NULL, TRUE, 'official', TRUE, 1, '{"parser_version": "moex_license_v1.0", "parsed_at": "2026-04-25T12:22:21+00:00", "source_pdf_sha1": "1e70fcf8ae3b", "answer_pdf_sha1": "aee6e6b22814", "source_family": "moex-gov-tw", "moex": {"exam_code": "112050", "c": "141", "s": "0904", "q": "1"}, "raw_section_label": "本試題為單一選擇題", "subject": "經濟學概要", "year": "112", "exam_name": "112年公務人員特種考試關務人員考試、身心障礙人員考試、國軍上校以上軍官轉任公務人員考試", "original_question_number": 33, "answer_corrected": false, "flags": [], "civil_slug": "customs", "civil_category": "一般行政"}'::jsonb, NULL),
  ('customs-7fec267e-moex-00155', 'customs-7fec267e', 'customs-7fec267e-moex-112-6948958a', 'sub-customs-7fec267e-01', NULL, 'single_choice', '有關總體景氣循環典型事實（stylizedfacts）之敘述，下列何者正確？', '["居住性投資支出為順景氣循環，且領先於景氣", "存貨變動投資支出為順景氣循環，且與景氣同時", "名目利率為順景氣循環，且與景氣同時", "通貨膨脹為反景氣循環，且落後於景氣"]'::jsonb, 0, NULL, TRUE, 'official', TRUE, 1, '{"parser_version": "moex_license_v1.0", "parsed_at": "2026-04-25T12:22:21+00:00", "source_pdf_sha1": "1e70fcf8ae3b", "answer_pdf_sha1": "aee6e6b22814", "source_family": "moex-gov-tw", "moex": {"exam_code": "112050", "c": "141", "s": "0904", "q": "1"}, "raw_section_label": "本試題為單一選擇題", "subject": "經濟學概要", "year": "112", "exam_name": "112年公務人員特種考試關務人員考試、身心障礙人員考試、國軍上校以上軍官轉任公務人員考試", "original_question_number": 34, "answer_corrected": false, "flags": [], "civil_slug": "customs", "civil_category": "一般行政"}'::jsonb, NULL)
